<h2></h2>
<h2><strong>Article</strong></h2>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Articles must have a title, consist of an introduction explaining in a short paragraph the When, Where, Who, What, Why. Followed with body where you'll need to put in all the details and explanations, along with your examples or illustrations. And finally, the only thing to be kept in mind is that any new idea or thought does not deserve a place in the conclusion. The conclusion is essentially a brief recap of the entire article, which signifies the end of the write-up.</p>

<h2><strong>Events</strong></h2>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Make sure you enter the necessary information in the event form to avoid delays before posting it. With the title, description, ticket prices, venue address, website and contact information, image with minimum dimensions of 500px by 200px and dates.</p>

<h2><strong>Competitions</strong></h2>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">It can include VJ/AV contests and battles, remixes, event and festival submissions, music videos competition and everything related to audio visual technology.</p>

<h2><strong>Projects</strong></h2>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">We want to hear from you and your latest projects, don't forget to include a title, description, when and where, who worked with you, your website and related links, images and/or videos.</p>

<h2><strong>Products</strong></h2>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Launching a new product? Or have something you want to send us.. Next thing you know it will be posted on the mag and may even be reviewed. Of course we suggest checking the site before posting us, to check if the product hasn't already been reviewed.</p>

<h2><strong>Jobs</strong></h2>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Your company has a position to offer related to audio video, design, arts or technology.</p>

<h2><strong>Courses &amp; Workshops</strong></h2>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Â Workshop or courses in the related and similar subjects: live softwares, post production, performance, electronics, design, integrated media, animation, technical and installations...</p>

<h2><strong>Videos</strong></h2>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Post us videos of your projects, we'll be posting it on <a href="http://www.vjstv.com/"><span style="color: #3366ff;">VJs TV</span></a> and maybe even VJs Mag.</p>";s:10:"post_title";s:6:"Submit";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:6:"submit";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2014-06-26 23:41:30";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2014-06-26 23:41:30";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:0;s:4:"guid";s:33:"http://www.vjsmag.com/?page_id=50";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:4:"page";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}}